00:10:17.480 --> 00:10:20.480
what do I need to do to inherit everlasting life?

00:10:20.480 --> 00:10:23.480
We can be sure that Jehovah will answer that prayer,

00:10:23.480 --> 00:10:26.480
maybe through personal study or Bible reading,

00:10:26.480 --> 00:10:29.480
or it might even be through a Samaritan.
